name: Ribbon Eco Grosgrain 1.5x50 yd
description:
Popular ECO Grosgrain ribbon is now available in and Eco version. Why send those old plastic bottles to the land fill when you can have ribbon made out of them. This ribbon is made out of old plastic bottles (100% post consumer recycled polyester). Be careful of our competitors products that may be made from a blend of post consumer and post industrial yarns.  When you buy this ribbon, you will be getting ribbon made entirely from recycled bottles in the USA.
Order ribbon by the roll.
Each roll is 100 or 50 yards as listed except 535354504 is available only as 50 yard roll.
